{
  "id": "019ce9ed-114b-7f51-89c2-d6460be59753",
  "content": "## Dashboard Completion — Features #7, #9, #10 (2026-03-14)\n\nAll 3 remaining dashboard roadmap features implemented, completing the 10/10 roadmap.\n\n### Feature #7: Live Session State\n- `GET /api/dashboard/sessions/live` endpoint: polls SessionManager::list_open(), joins agent names, computes pending entries and duration\n- `LiveSessionsBar` component at top of Agents tab: session pills with state-colored dots (Active=mint, Stale=amber), 5-second polling via usePoll, auto-hides when empty\n- SessionRecord.created_at is DateTime<Utc> — duration computed via direct arithmetic, not string parsing\n\n### Feature #9: OTEL Span Drill-Down\n- `OtelContextLayer` in corvia-telemetry: custom tracing::Layer that reads tracing_opentelemetry::OtelData from span extensions, extracts trace_id/span_id/parent_span_id, stores as OtelFields\n- Layer composition order: registry → env_filter → otel_layer → context_layer → fmt_layer (OTEL must populate OtelData before context layer reads it)\n- ParsedTrace::Span gained trace_id/span_id/parent_span_id as Option<String> for backward compatibility\n- `collect_trace_trees()` in traces.rs: groups spans by trace_id, builds parent-child trees via HashMap + recursive build_tree function, computes start_offset_ms via chrono DateTime delta\n- `GET /api/dashboard/traces/recent?limit=N` endpoint\n- `WaterfallView` component: trace list sidebar + nested horizontal bars color-coded by module, graceful \"Enable OTEL exporter\" degradation\n- SpanStats enhanced with p50/p95/p99 percentiles computed from rolling window, sort-once optimization\n\n### Feature #10: GC Operations Dashboard\n- GcReport expanded from 1 to 7 fields: orphans_rolled_back, duration_ms, stale_transitioned, closed_sessions_cleaned, agents_suspended, entries_deduplicated, started_at. Added serde::Serialize/Deserialize derives.\n- GcHistory: in-memory Mutex<VecDeque<GcReport>> ring buffer (max 50), stored as Arc<GcHistory> on AppState\n- gc_run() wrapper adds Instant::now() timing and ensures started_at is populated\n- `GET /api/dashboard/gc` and `POST /api/dashboard/gc/run` endpoints with gc_report_to_dto() conversion helper (avoids orphan rule by using plain function instead of From impl)\n- `GcPanel` component: last-run stats cards, SVG sparkline history (color-coded by orphan count), \"Run GC Now\" trigger button with error handling and immediate feedback via triggerResult state\n\n### Architecture Decisions\n- OtelData approach (not Context::current()): OtelData.builder has the current span's own IDs, while Context::current() only has the parent's context during on_new_span\n- gc_report_to_dto() function instead of From<GcReport> for GcReportDto: Rust orphan rule forbids impl From<ForeignType> for OtherForeignType in a third crate\n- GC is manual-only: scheduled=false, no periodic timer. GcPanel shows \"Manual trigger only\"\n- usePoll returns { data, error, loading } only — no refresh function. GcPanel uses local state for immediate trigger feedback\n\n### New Files (4)\n- crates/corvia-telemetry/src/otel_context_layer.rs\n- tools/corvia-dashboard/src/components/LiveSessionsBar.tsx\n- tools/corvia-dashboard/src/components/GcPanel.tsx\n- tools/corvia-dashboard/src/components/WaterfallView.tsx\n\n### New Endpoints (4)\n- GET /api/dashboard/gc\n- POST /api/dashboard/gc/run\n- GET /api/dashboard/sessions/live\n- GET /api/dashboard/traces/recent?limit=N\n\n### Test Coverage\n- 15 new tests across kernel (3), common (2), server (8), telemetry (2)\n- All 80 server tests pass, frontend builds clean (26 modules)",
